            "advisory": "Affected versions of the nltk package are vulnerable to Denial of Service (DoS) due to missing authentication on a shutdown function in the WordNet Browser HTTP server. In nltk.app.wordnet_app, HTTPServer((\"\", port), MyServerHandler) listens on all interfaces by default, and the request handler checks whether the decoded path equals SHUTDOWN THE SERVER; when server_mode=False in the default runBrowser=True mode, that path triggers os._exit(0) and immediately terminates the process.",
