            "advisory": "Affected versions of the nltk package are vulnerable to Cross-site Scripting (XSS) due to improper output encoding of user-controlled input. In nltk.app.wordnet_app, requests to the lookup_... route are processed through page_from_href() and page_from_reference(), where the decoded word value is inserted into the HTML response without html.escape(), specifically in the \"The word or words '%s' were not found in the dictionary.\" % word code path.",
